additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Vine Fruits (27%) (Sultanas, Raisins), Sugar, Wheat Flour, Tropical Rum Punch Sauce (11%) (Sugar, Mango Puree, Water, Rum, Passionfruit Juice from Concentrate, Pineapple Juice from Concentrate, Cornflour, Natural Flavourings, Lemon Juice from Concentrate, Preservative (Potassium Sorbate), Natural Colour (Carotene)), Rum (8.5%), Cider (6%) (Preservative (224)), Candied Pineapple Slice (4%) (Pineapple, Glucose-fructose Syrup, Acidity Regulator (330), Preservative (Sulphur Dioxide)), Non Hydrogenated Vegetable Oils (Palm Oil**, Rice Flour, Sunflower Oil), Dried Diced Pineapple (3.5%) (Pineapple, Sugar, Acidity Regulator (330), Preservative (Sulphur Dioxide)), Humectant (422), Water, Treacle, Candied Mixed Peel (Orange Peel, Glucose-fructose Syrup, Lemon Peel, Sugar, Acidity Regulator (330), Preservative (Sulphur Dioxide)), Cream (Milk), Salt, Allspice, Mixed Spice, Cinnamon, Nutmeg, Yeast, Orange Oil, Emulsifiers (471, 472e), Wheat Protein, Vinegar, Lemon Oil, Rapeseed Oil, Palm Oil**, Palm Fat**.Contains 1.4mL alcohol per 100g of pudding.

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: May Contain TREE NUTS, Contains CEREALS CONTAINING GLUTEN, Contains MILK

description: A tropical Christmas Pudding packed with vine fruits, diced pineapple, cider and rum. Finished with whole candied pineapple slice and a hidden spiced rum punch center.
name: Spiced Rum Pudding
